graph LR
    TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service Operator]

    %% External Platform Dependencies (Required)
    TrustyAI -->|required| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.19+]
    TrustyAI -->|TLS certificates| CertMgr[cert-manager or service-ca]

    %% External Platform Dependencies (Optional)
    TrustyAI -.->|OAuth, Routes, TLS| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.6+]
    TrustyAI -.->|metrics collection| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v1]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|watches & patches| KServe[KServe<br/>InferenceServices v1alpha1/v1beta1<br/>ServingRuntimes]
    TrustyAI -->|env var injection| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving<br/>label: modelmesh-service=modelmesh-serving]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI integration| TrustyAI

    %% External Services
    TrustyAI -->|image pull| Registry[Container Registries<br/>quay.io<br/>registry.redhat.io]
    TrustyAI -->|OAuth validation| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server]

    %% Storage
    TrustyAI -->|creates PVCs| Storage[Persistent Storage<br/>Kubernetes PVs]

    %% Managed Workload Dependencies
    TrustyAIService[TrustyAI Service<br/>Managed Workload]
    TrustyAI -->|deploys & manages| TrustyAIService
    TrustyAIService -->|stores data| Storage
    TrustyAIService -->|receives payloads| ModelMesh

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes metrics| TrustyAIService

    %% Kubernetes API
    K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    TrustyAI -->|CRUD operations| K8sAPI
    Kubernetes -->|provides| K8sAPI

    %% service-ca integration
    ServiceCA[service-ca Controller]
    OpenShift -->|provides| ServiceCA
    ServiceCA -->|injects certs| TrustyAIService

    %% Styling
    style TrustyAI fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff
    style Kubernetes fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style OpenShift fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style CertMgr fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PrometheusOp fill:#e6522c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ModelMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Registry fill:#40b4e5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthServer fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Storage fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style TrustyAIService fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Prometheus fill:#e6522c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style K8sAPI fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
